
to download the files please 


1- open a terminal in linux and clone the files using "git clone https://github.com/TheC4esar/cowrie.git" then run cowrie1.sh then cowrie2.sh

2- after we are in the cowrie user we are downloading cowrie using "git clone https://github.com/cowrie/cowrie.git"
cd cowrie/

then

3- Continue the documentation right from step4 :

virtualenv --python=python3 cowrie-env
then..
pip install --upgrade pip
pip install --upgrade -r requirements.txt

4- to start cowrie:
bin/cowrie start



docs : https://cowrie.readthedocs.io/en/latest/INSTALL.html#step-1-install-system-dependencies